.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Color: blue, green, red, white, yellow
City: new-york, san-francisco, venice, prague, nizza
Birthday: november, march, july, february, may
Cigar: bluemaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
Job: nurseerman, dancer, dressmaker, nurse, librarian
1. City:new-york == Color:red
2. City:swedish == Job:dressmaker
3. City:san-francisco == Birthday:february
4. Color:green is on the left of Color:white
5. Color:green == Birthday:march
6. Cigar:pall-mall == Job:dancer
7. Color:yellow == Cigar:dunhill
8. Birthday:july is in the middle
9. City:prague is on the far left
10. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Job:nurseerman
11. Job:librarians is on the left or right of Cigar:dunhill
12. Cigar:bluemaster == Birthday:november
13. City:venice == Cigar:prince
14. City:prague is on the left or right of Color:blue
15. Cigar:blend is on the left or right of Birthday:may

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    yellow	|     blue	|      red	|     green	|     white	|
| City	|   prague	|    san-francisco	|    new-york	|    venice	|    swedish	|
| Job		|     nurseerman	|    librarian	|     dancer	|     nurse	|      dressmaker	|
| Birthday	|    may	|     february	|     july	|    march	|      november	|
| Cigar		|   dunhill	|    blend	|  pall-mall	|    prince	|   bluemaster	|
